.DT
zap_stat_cache
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
zap_stat_cache

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
zap_stat_cache -  This method zaps the stat cache when a certain stat changes.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void zap_stat_cache()
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/skills.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method zaps the stat cache when a certain stat changes.
It calls the function stats_to_zap() on the living object to
figure out which stats have changed.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
/std/living/stats->stats_to_zap()

.EP

